Package com.clarkparsia.openrdf.query

This package contains classes for working with OpenRdf query objects.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
BooleanQueryResult An analog to TupleQueryResult and GraphQueryResult, this represents the result to a Boolean/Ask query.
 

Class Summary
AbstractBooleanQueryResultWriter BooleanQueryResultWriter base for creating custom writer implementations which throws UnsupportedOperationException exceptions for the non-boolean result format methods which are incorrectly in the QueryResultWriter interface.
AbstractQueryResultWriter More useful base for creating custom QueryResultWriter implementations.
BooleanQueryResultImpl Default implementation of a BooleanQueryResult
DelegatingGraphQueryResult Base class for creating a GraphQueryResult decorator which delegates all calls to the child result.
DelegatingTupleQueryResult Base class for creating a TupleQueryResult decorator which delegates all calls to its child TupleQueryResult
SesameQueryUtils Collection of utility methods for working with the OpenRdf Sesame Query API.
 

Package com.clarkparsia.openrdf.query Description

This package contains classes for working with OpenRdf query objects. It includes utilities for rendering, building, modifying, and executing SPARQL & SeRQL queries.
